oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Elk Avenue decorated
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Photograph of Elk Avenue with holiday decorations. Signs for Nave's Hardware, Fair's Jewelers, Tate's, and Fred Davis Jewelers are seen. A Pepsi billboard that reads "Pepsi, Come Alive! You're in the Pepsi Generation!" is on top of building on the right.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:source: Looking Back at Tennessee Photograph Collection, 1890-1981
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Christmas decorations; Streets; Billboards
